

BESES

   This word is from the Spanish veces.

   beses
   times

   isang beses
   one time, once

   dalawang beses
   two times, twice

   maraming beses
   many times

   Anuman ang gagawin, pitong beses isipin.
   What you do, think about it seven times.

   Easier Filipino version of:
   Bago muna gawin, makapitong isipin.
